{"tid":318161,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"hk express 同一件行李，去程時話無問題，回程時話有問題要罰錢","createTime":"2017-07-12T02:06:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-13T09:16:42.000Z","uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ab1e44381a15eaaf0eef613e3c24741d63adc871","tid":318161,"uid":63075,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:06:08.000Z","msg":"我去果度得hk express  有從香港直飛去目的地<br />\n其他航空公司無航線<br />\n所以請唔好亂屌人貪平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次坐哩間野就咁<br />\n<br />\n明明買好晒行李，去果時係香港機場都問清楚話無問題<br />\n<br />\n點知回程果時係日本果邊就話唔得，要比1萬日元先比上機 （話太長）<br />\n<br />\n咁都得？<br />\n我同佢講話從香港果邊過黎係無問題，<br />\n點知佢答「我地哩個機場係咁，香港得唔代表哩度得」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係度只係想提醒大家小心哩d陷阱<br />\n如果其他公司有航線實唔坐哩間</span>"},{"pid":"598e165b8090c56f6be41e82de9aaae1e89b178e","tid":318161,"uid":28654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:08:27.000Z","msg":"圖?"},{"pid":"138f288a89144f69baf766b88b95d4c5e1793afd","tid":318161,"uid":107156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:09:33.000Z","msg":"佢有冇答過你日本都得先, 又真係每個機場都唔同wo"},{"pid":"1190377d4d92b6b4f81cc36dab6334c4a6799333","tid":318161,"uid":112583,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:10:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">抵</span></span><br />\n自己唔做功課怪邊個"},{"pid":"b82db4438dc4393bb84c672d441b687fba850210","tid":318161,"uid":57062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:10:33.000Z","msg":"認真答， 日本捉得特別緊。"},{"pid":"f77681cef00be4aa5698483f6c2cddf1e71914c1","tid":318161,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:12:46.000Z","msg":"下體會自大<br />\n<br />\n即係下體過長？"},{"pid":"9bc51a41f5d842900446c1e3822f609f59bab2ee","tid":318161,"uid":3900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:13:15.000Z","msg":"ＵＯ係外port捉到緊<br />\n特別係日本，人地跟規舉做嘢啫<br />\n<br />\n香港就廢Ｑ事煩，佢有斟情權住俾你過得就過"},{"pid":"23d8c91