\" /> 同埋你夠膽話你去完旅行無再買嘢放入去？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n長度呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6275df21c383ad5b266fa1352b5ede4914e7ae1","tid":318161,"uid":103591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:25:12.000Z","msg":"我有興趣知你個行李咩尺寸同你從邊個機場返？講出來等大家都可以以後小心下。<br />\n<br />\nHKEXPRESS 就要託運行李長闊高158cm 以內，收你一萬yen即係當咗特大行李？"},{"pid":"d1ed129b2cb0581605b77d90d7a2deb4845a607f","tid":318161,"uid":103591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T02:27:28.000Z","msg":"同埋如果係其他航空公司，你都要睇佢尺寸有唔同限制。"},{"pid":"6fa3137b1e0b7d54f5fa9669ed1816b3c8bf6751","tid":318161,"uid":34692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:36:01.000Z","msg":"咁下次香港都捉得咁嚴會唔會好啲？ 啱你班港豬？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0911494a053ffb9e5e0fc0997e656a5c8b417764","tid":318161,"uid":51399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:38:54.000Z","msg":"睇咗好耐先明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad6b1bd0f60c197f5d12ec5a4344020daee591e2","tid":318161,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:41:45.000Z","msg":"去程10kg 回程40kg?"},{"pid":"eb24070d165547dcab3f12c0ecbee7fd5737b208","tid":318161,"uid":9708,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:41:45.000Z","msg":"去程10kg 回程40kg?"},{"pid":"7c72b83b1ed2dd336791d382c367231dd3cc7999","tid":318161,"uid":2772,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T04:50:32.000Z","msg":"咁追罰番香港果程囉<br />\n條氣會唔會順d?<br />\n<br />\n自己衰仲嫌三嫌四<br />\n<br />\n唔該你出街講普通話添<br />\n唔好影衰哂"},{"pid":"9d8a187a979cc9e8c052c2d4ce395deb8bfd0637","tid":318161,"uid":43545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:46:38.000Z","msg":"認真答<br />\n香港飛果程差少少通常俾你過<br />\n<br />\n日本回程既話<br />\n因為UO 係判俾第二間公司做<br />\n人地職員唔知你可以點寬限<br />\n會跟足指引做<br />\n所以回程會緊D"},{"pid":"ca083ea164d2a6c82ab7f59522499aa042b026cb","tid":318161,"uid":51399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:51:55.000Z","msg":"講緊件行李過長下話? 樓上嗰兩件答乜春嗲"},{"pid":"a22bf1b8e7f36aaf3ca0316be4cb5159eec42119","tid":318161,"uid":65328,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:55:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去果度得hk express  有從香港直飛去目的地<br />\n其他航空公司無航線<br />\n所以請唔好亂屌人貪平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次坐哩間野就咁<br />\n<br />\n明明買好晒行李，去果時係香港機場都問清楚話無問題<br />\n<br />\n點知回程果時係日本果邊就話唔得，要比1萬日元先比上機 （話太長）<br />\n<br />\n咁都得？<br />\n我同佢講話從香港果邊過黎係無問題，<br />\n點知佢答「我地哩個機場係咁，香港得唔代表哩度得」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係度只係想提醒大家小心哩d陷阱<br />\n如果其他公司有航線實唔坐哩間</span></blockquote><br />\n咪即係貪平囉， 一萬日元都俾唔起， 唔講以為無得轉機。<br />\n<br />\n長闊高都叫陷阱唔好搭飛機啦"},{"pid":"254cd4ab54e5254daa315fafe13c2de4fd24dd50","tid":318161,"uid":24833,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:58:16.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，坐廉航就收撚皮啦，衰撚左仲擺上黎講，死窮撚"},{"pid":"260f6ba00ef8311f75896417a4bd6efdf4b724cb","tid":318161,"uid":52943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T05:58:22.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣都叫陷阱食屎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"244acacec7c0f771ba0249bce37fe38a72b28308","tid":318161,"uid":121251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:08:30.000Z","msg":"收皮啦垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3ecbd0a2207febd311b42b8adccef3dac0057cb","tid":318161,"uid":281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:38:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b32ae52318a9d497d144af75f13e139b49674003","tid":318161,"uid":35420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T06:39:23.000Z","msg":"垃圾咪去旅行影衰香港人"},{"pid":"5e3f5a08ca8c65c6982a0281546967150a779b68","tid":318161,"uid":14509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:12:44.000Z","msg":"Uo日本port係外判俾ana做ground<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要屌請屌返日本公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71ab33231c8efaaa43f35ebc993d6e9db6d69bda","tid":318161,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:15:30.000Z","msg":"係成田見唔少樓豬咁既人比人罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8193aff5df65e0d4ab1d4596de93d4beaac864da","tid":318161,"uid":56219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:16:51.000Z","msg":"HKEXPRESS 日本係幾緊幾認真下..."},{"pid":"a71b7ebb73067c4f66af93ab9a5cb488926aa0db","tid":318161,"uid":103591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:36:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係成田見唔少樓豬咁既人比人罰錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n坐UO又真係差唔多次次在日本check-in 時，附近都有人有唔同程度的行李相關爭議。"},{"pid":"09849c14d7c31ceca145096066bdaf2bbdd88333","tid":318161,"uid":103591,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:45:55.000Z","msg":"咁當然人地都寫到明行李重量同大小，如果係要搏人放過你，不如守規則。好多時就係有人唔守規則攪到寄倉都要等一餐....<br />\n<br />\n最好大家都按行李尺寸規定，同排隊寄倉前自己磅過唔超重 （我就用旅行磅仔，個磅仔只重53g），一定快手好多。"},{"pid":"b345520c078216670395f26ac21d501d2e3b67e0","tid":318161,"uid":17692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:46:12.000Z","msg":"因為hkexpress 會捉得好緊d agent 少少野都會罰agent錢<br />\n<br />\nCheap公司黎 錢又唔係比得多 但要求多多果隻<br />\n<br />\n廉航的生存之道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99c22cb3e74ef8b6b6c2184b07fbd02149a95ded","tid":318161,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:48:33.000Z","msg":"純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a83753cda8f6b35c08f1ea4797e8c9abaa5e2c6","tid":318161,"uid":33730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T07:59:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>純文字討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓豬俾人屌到潛左水啦"},{"pid":"fee340bbdac02a9861ead18d4fb40b5110eb3ecd","tid":318161,"uid":38143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:04:30.000Z","msg":"Hkexpress 飛日本但做獨市唔係好多機場架啫<br />\n高松定石垣島？"},{"pid":"a6f26398dc91aa8a6022b3ad2ce6734558ec9f52","tid":318161,"uid":92743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去果度得hk express  有從香港直飛去目的地<br />\n其他航空公司無航線<br />\n所以請唔好亂屌人貪平<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次坐哩間野就咁<br />\n<br />\n明明買好晒行李，去果時係香港機場都問清楚話無問題<br />\n<br />\n點知回程果時係日本果邊就話唔得，要比1萬日元先比上機 （話太長）<br />\n<br />\n咁都得？<br />\n我同佢講話從香港果邊過黎係無問題，<br />\n點知佢答「我地哩個機場係咁，香港得唔代表哩度得」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係度只係想提醒大家小心哩d陷阱<br />\n如果其他公司有航線實唔坐哩間</span></blockquote><br />\n坐你老味"},{"pid":"0119db1ee593896dcd80944e78583c244310542d","tid":318161,"uid":33787,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:08:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fc1212aae7ac4fde37cc57bda0534403c6a409e4","tid":318161,"uid":105531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:10:55.000Z","msg":"有圖有真相 放把尺喺你太長果一面畀大家睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"715ba1d483860203844d035d785653fd4f589626","tid":318161,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:14:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點知回程果時係日本果邊就話唔得，要比1萬日元先比上機 （話太長）<br />\n</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主你邊度太長？"},{"pid":"3aaad1781cc8e52157a32d91294ecccf6d8cc627","tid":318161,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:16:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係度只係想提醒大家小心哩d陷阱<br />\n如果其他公司有航線實唔坐哩間</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係廉航你捨得幫襯？"},{"pid":"9623cb894b3659edc6429b8f3130516bd4e93cd4","tid":318161,"uid":44377,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:36:28.000Z","msg":"喂唔好潛水先啦, 可唔可以話我知你邊個機場返同埋件行李幾長呀"},{"pid":"64492e0dc711303ff76770276cb4b44e016a0c0e","tid":318161,"uid":36087,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>去程10kg 回程40kg?</blockquote><br />\n屌你老尾而家文盲都學人上網、上連登？<br />\n我唔是話樓主一定冇錯，因為我唔知長度標準<br />\n不過人地話明捉過長，你唔撚係問人有冇重左下話？"},{"pid":"b69def739d6bd1cf8fab0cb57df246a4b90952b1","tid":318161,"uid":26354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:42:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去程10kg 回程40kg?</blockquote><br />\n屌你老尾而家文盲都學人上網、上連登？<br />\n我唔是話樓主一定冇錯，因為我唔知長度標準<br />\n不過人地話明捉過長，你唔撚係問人有冇重左下話？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10d5bc2de8afe6a0b2984dc3614800ccaf58cbf2","tid":318161,"uid":35178,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:43:15.000Z","msg":"次次坐UO飛成田都被ANA話個Backpack太大，要求下佢先比我過。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b859afec97174f28b9fb9cc29a22e5a330850531","tid":318161,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T08:48:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hkexpress 飛日本但做獨市唔係好多機場架啫<br />\n高松定石垣島？</blockquote><br />\n最緊要知咩黎， 點解需要帶"},{"pid":"5f35938b8597dd2c66f3b74219ad539587958867","tid":318161,"uid":82562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:09:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f776b88ae0368460f1677c97227648be087d0cfb","tid":318161,"uid":31108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:32:12.000Z","msg":"香港比你過係人情 <br />\n日本唔比你過係道理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想當日香港要收你錢<br />\n睇你都會一樣開post架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b3dc28238c0cc86dd986156fd878289d58c4ea","tid":318161,"uid":85762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:49:58.000Z","msg":"你有買行李佢無叫你寄倉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上次去完富士山拎住碌行山竹佢都主動叫我寄倉。<br />\n話太長唔比上機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"602ec44b673cab23707041e6c600dc95e869ae63","tid":318161,"uid":7766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:55:25.000Z","msg":"28寸GIP 得唔得嫁其實"},{"pid":"a7e84d5f4ce11b4060fdd261028ada40426fffc6","tid":318161,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:58:58.000Z","msg":"我想問香港飛o個時有冇度你行李？"},{"pid":"ff56a282614048e32e25bfa77a68cba63c24b064","tid":318161,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T09:59:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Hkexpress 飛日本但做獨市唔係好多機場架啫<br />\n高松定石垣島？</blockquote><br />\n仲有廣島?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fc8d3ccfd5bc383cde411b2e90016573f2d0d22","tid":318161,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:01:10.000Z","msg":"XX係人情..."},{"pid":"36f20a7d62628581386071b0fc2174032be0514f","tid":318161,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T10:05:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>28寸GIP 