<br />\n日本番黎咪比人捉<br />\n我直情唔知自己有帶"},{"pid":"74f9c5e1fcc8b19855c890662f1fe611e5b72412","tid":318161,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:01:09.000Z","msg":"上次泰國清邁handcarry 過磅超 o.5 kg 無事無加 $, 照上到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5778c8f7290fa7179d56be6fe6239af314f99b49","tid":318161,"uid":65406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:04:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>上次泰國清邁handcarry 過磅超 o.5 kg 無事無加 $, 照上到機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n情況其實一樣。如果捉得緊你唔好彩。鬆咪賺<br />\n之前搭香草起候機室。D地勤真係遂個捉住上磅加計件數"},{"pid":"5f1888f9a398c6cb541e625eec2a430fe6e2d348","tid":318161,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:05:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2938d86006741632d20307e7d2f482d0a0196544","tid":318161,"uid":103591,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:13:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>28寸GIP 得唔得嫁其實</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n寄倉要睇一件行李長闊高加埋是否少於158cm ，我個28就剛好157，唔同牌可能有少少分別。<br />\n<br />\n我以前試過問UO佢手提行李尺寸，網上佢寫56*36*23，我個手提就55*40*20 佢都係EMAIL將網頁上呢個尺寸覆返我，但我都係唔知我闊咗3cm(但長度短1cm 同深度短返3cm 得唔得。咁我之後都試帶上機，一直又無人（香港、日本）話過我個喼唔可以手提"},{"pid":"011991a1d1aa82f6b2f0afdcb939a62b2f1ce2c6","tid":318161,"uid":8040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都戇撚鳩<br />\n唔捉係人情<br />\n捉你係道理啦<br />\n<br />\n我係香港搭<br />\n較剪同𠝹刀都上到機<br />\n<br />\n日本番黎咪比人捉<br />\n我直情唔知自己有帶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我上次係台灣連係筆袋較眼鏡嘅細螺絲批都比人沒收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我同佢講話香港都check 唔到<br />\n佢覆我話我們台灣比較厲害<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3371fb5cac143e659b2faad42484f8aa4116696b","tid":318161,"uid":65328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T11:34:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><b